Usage: editChangeMask [-help] {-to {0 1 2} | [[-top {0 1 2}] [-bottom {0 1 2}] [-cut {0 1 2}]] | -trim_metal {0 1 2}}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-bottom {0 1 2}         # Specifies the mask color for the bottom layer of
                        # selected vias. (enum, optional)
-cut {0 1 2}            # Specifies the mask color for the cut layer of
                        # selected vias. (enum, optional)
-to {0 1 2}             # Specifies the mask color for the selected wires or
                        # physical pins. (enum, optional)
-top {0 1 2}            # Specifies the mask color for the top layer of
                        # selected vias. (enum, optional)
-trim_metal {0 1 2}     # Specifies the mask color for the trim metal.
                        # (enum, optional)